  "detailed_description": "Sorcerer's Tournament is a turn-based RPG with mini-games for training your character, gameplay is focused on growing and improving between each duel. <br>As you win duels and tournaments you will permanently unlock new spells, modes and difficulties. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.poster.avif?t=1640205415\" width=640 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.webm?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.mp4?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Winning Through Sheer Force Is Not The Only Option</h2> In this game's duels you will face opponents that might out-last you rather than out-damage you.<br><br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.poster.avif?t=1640205415\" width=640 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.webm?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.mp4?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Train Your Student And Manage Your Time Carefully</h2>Use the time you have to train carefully as an extra damage might not be as important as learning that new spell.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features Include</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  learn unique spells that can fuse with modifiers into 110 spell combinations<br></li><li>  choose the school and student <br></li><li> play challenging mini-games training each major stat<br></li><li> unlock special game modes<br></li><li> fight magic battles to your heart's content!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Sorcerer's Tournament is a turn-based RPG with mini-games for training your character, gameplay is focused on growing and improving between each duel. <br>As you win duels and tournaments you will permanently unlock new spells, modes and difficulties. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.poster.avif?t=1640205415\" width=640 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.webm?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/f83130de447be1756fdc38d1f092fc2b.mp4?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Winning Through Sheer Force Is Not The Only Option</h2> In this game's duels you will face opponents that might out-last you rather than out-damage you.<br><br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.poster.avif?t=1640205415\" width=640 height=104 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.webm?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822940/extras/3aa731c001cce842aa4c7d925fe12a57.mp4?t=1640205415\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Train Your Student And Manage Your Time Carefully</h2>Use the time you have to train carefully as an extra damage might not be as important as learning that new spell.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features Include</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  learn unique spells that can